      • upsert

        public OrientDbUpdateStatement<E> upsert()
        Description copied from interface: FeatureUpsert
        Marks the statement as UPSERT meaning that it is an insert of the object does not exist and an update if the object already exists. An UPSERT requires a WHERE clause.
        Specified by:
